cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.CL, cs.LG 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image analysis and style compatibility between furniture items. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also likely as the paper uses a joint image-text embedding method for querying stylistically compatible furniture items based on text attributes. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with analyzing and comparing images of furniture items. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a possible category as the paper uses text attributes to constrain the image analysis. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses Siamese networks and pretrained CNNs for efficient style compatibility assessment.
